body.name: Samsonite Hardside Spinner Wheel Luggage, Silver, 2-Piece Set
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery February 21 - 23. Order within 13 hrs 48 mins.
features: Luggage set includes 20" Carry-On and 24" Checked Hardside Spinner Luggage and features an ABS hardshell exterior that is durable against wear and tear from traveling; Keeps your belongings safe and sound in the airplane or in the ground
Checked luggage and carry on luggage both have an adjustable pull handle with a comfortable grip and double spinner wheels for easy mobility through airports
Organizing your belongings is made easier with the half-and-half split opening and an interior blouse within each hard luggage to keep your garments wrinkle-free
Shoe compartments for the carry on luggage help maintain order within your luggage when you are attending multiple events that require differing footwear
Each hardshell luggage can provide 1.5 inches of extra space when you need it to take home souvenirs from your trips or when you need a lot of clothing and stuff to take with you
Carry-on Case Dimensions: 20.5" x 13.8" x 8.5", Upright Case Dimensions: 25.5" x 17.7" x 11.5"
body.description: Book that flight to your next destination and pack all of your essentials in this 2 piece, featuring a 20" Carry-On and 24" Checked Hardside, this New Castle Hardside and Expandable Luggage with Spinner Wheels from Samsonite. This suitcase set has an exterior that is carefully constructed from a tough ABS shell which is capable of resisting damage from wear and tear wherever you go. This exterior will keep your belongings safe from bumps during your flight for a worry-free travel experience. This exterior is also easy to maintain as it only needs to be wiped with a damp cloth for easy aftercare. Each hard sided luggage with spinner wheels features an adjustable pull handle with a comfortable grip for your convenience. The aforementioned wheels are double-spinner which ensures they are stable and roll smoothly through airports or on city streets without any issues. These hard suitcases with wheels showcase an easy way to be opened with the user-friendly large zipper pulls when you need to take out something quickly. Each hardshell luggage has a half-and-half interior split opening for a better way of organizing your essentials. In addition, there is also an interior blouse within each hard luggage to keep your garments wrinkle-free. Built-in shoe pockets within the carry-on luggage are helpful for trips that require multiple shoes for different events. Worry less about running out of usable area to put souvenirs or extra stuff in these suit cases as they both can expand up to 1.5 inches of extra space. Prepare to travel to your next destination with style and safety in mind with these 2 pieces of hardsided Samsonite luggage that can be with you wherever you go. Carry-on Case Dimensions: 20.5" x 13.8" x 8.5" Carry-on Overall Dimensions (including wheels): 22" x 14" x 9" Overall Weight: 5.6 lbs. Upright Case Dimensions: 25.5" x 17.7" x 11.5" Upright Overall Dimensions (including wheels): 27" x 18.5" x 12" Overall Weight: 8.7 lbs Shipping Dimensions in Carton: 28.15" x 19" x 12.2" Shipping Weight: 15.2 lbs

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Samsonite New Castle The New Castle 2-Piece Set (20" carry on and 24" checked piece) is perfect for any trip with two spinners; one to carry on and one to check. You can pack all your travel needs in these rugged hardside cases.
Expand Your Horizons Featuring a 1.5" expansion for extra packing capacity for those last minute items.

Handle The pull handle adjusts to provide comfort when traveling. Interior Organization A roomy interior with shoe pockets on the carry on only, helps you maintain tidiness. Double Wheels Wear-tested double spinner wheels deliver maximum stability.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars "Samsonite Midnight Navy Spinner Set: Stylish, Durable, and Perfect for Extended Journeys!"
reviews.reviewText: The Samsonite Hardside Spinner Wheel Luggage set in Midnight Navy is an absolute travel game-changer! The value for this 2-piece set is unbeatable, offering durability and style. The spinner wheels glide effortlessly, making navigation through airports and streets a breeze. Recently used it for a 20-day vacation, and the ample space and organization made packing a joy. Samsonite has truly nailed it with this set—robust, chic, and practical. An excellent investment for any avid traveler!

reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Wrong info on description.
reviews.reviewText: These are nice hard shell Samsonite suitcases, however be aware of errors in the description. The larger one is NOT 24 inches, but 26 inches and is expandable. The smaller one is in fact 20 inches, but it is NOT expandable...the discrepancies might or might not be critical to certain buyers, but they are noteworthy and should be corrected by the seller.
